, 405\n|-\n| [[Skylake (microarchitecture)|Skylake]] - 1151 || i3/5/7-'''6'''000 ||(G)4000 || 3900 and 3800 || rowspan=\"2\" | 9th || HD 510, 515, 520, 530 and 535; Iris 540 and 550; Iris Pro 580 || rowspan=\"7\" | 1.1 Mesa 18.1 ||rowspan=\"7\" | 1.1<ref>{{cite web|url=https://downloadcenter.intel.com/download/29074/Intel-Graphics-Windows-10-DCH-Drivers|title=DRIVER VERSION: 26.20.100.7212|website=Downloadmirror.intel.com|accessdate=September 25, 2019}}</ref> || rowspan=7 | 4.6<ref>{{cite web|url=https://downloadcenter.intel.com/download/29074/Intel-Graphics-Windows-10-DCH-Drivers|title=DRIVER VERSION: 26.20.100.7212 |website=Downloadmirror.intel.com|accessdate=September 25, 2019}}</ref> || rowspan=\"7\" | 12 ([[Direct3D Feature Levels|fl&nbsp;12_1]])|| rowspan=\"7\" | 6.0 || 2.0 (Beignet)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Intel-Beignet-1.3-Released|title=Beignet 1.3 Released With OpenCL 2.0 Support |author=Michael Larabel |date=20 January 2017 |website=[[Phoronix]]}}</ref> / 2.1 (Neo)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Intel-New-Compute-Runtime|title=Intel Open-Sources LLVM Graphics Compiler, Compute Runtime With OpenCL 2.1+ |author=Michael Larabel |date=16 February 2018 |website=[[Phoronix]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Apollo Lake]] - SoCs || {{N/A}} || (J/N)4xxx || (J/N)3xxx || HD Graphics 500, 505 || rowspan=\"2\" | 2.0 (Beignet)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Intel-Beignet-1.3-Released|title=Beignet 1.3 Released With OpenCL 2.0 Support |author=Michael Larabel |date=20 January 2017 |website=[[Phoronix]]}}</ref> / 1.2 (Neo)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://github.com/intel/compute-runtime/commit/7e9ad412908a4a16ce10f6512f13147e80dd8040#diff-04c6e90faac2675aa89e2176d2eec7d8|title=Initial Commit |author=Brandon Fliflet |date= 21 December 2017 |website=[[GitHub]]}}</ref>\n|- style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"\n| [[Gemini Lake]] - SoCs || {{N/A}} || Silver (J/N)5xxx || (J/N)